{"tid":1723354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於火魔裝修 大家要諗清楚個風險 入嚟睇下","createTime":"2019-11-15T07:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:36:05.000Z","uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8221180b7934cf704adb0b2dea7abc2dc89f7178","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"上個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1721644/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1721644/page/1</a><br />\n有巴打屌我標題唔好 所以改咗<br />\n<br />\n未睇過可以睇睇上個post先<br />\n睇過嘅唔該幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>上個post講緊用火魔裝修失咗控燒咗上民居（有幾單）<br />\nPOPO做嘅殺人放火 我哋唔好硬食 大家要有共識同文宣組溝通<br />\n我哋係有良知嘅人 我哋唔想見到殺咗無辜嘅人<br />\n我哋唔係對家班狗 我哋要保持理性<br />\n借鑑歷史 唔好傷害無辜<br />\n<br />\n黃同白嘅比例絕對高過藍同黑<br />\n機率嚟講係會傷到自己人高啲<br />\n<br />\n我哋笑POPO係毅進仔殺人犯嘅時候<br />\n我哋係咪要做返同一樣野？<br />\n我哋唔係暴徒！<br />\n笑佢哋唔理性失控 我哋就要保持理性<br />\n唔好變成暴徒popo<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚係咪一定要用難控制嘅火？<br />\n用其他魔法係咪唔得？<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上個post嘅一啲總結：<br />\n1. 有巴打提議當我哋有共識時可以請民間記者會幫手出聲明<br />\n2. 如果有手足用錯魔法 各位禮貌提點<br />\n3. 滅火隊 如果有POPO做就幫手救 街坊裝就得<br />\n<br />\n我哋抗爭嘅同時 唔應該傷害無辜市民 佢哋好可能係手足嘅親人同朋友<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅人生賭晒喺呢場運動<br />\n天上手足嘅真相<br />\n被捕手足受到嘅傷害<br />\n要認真諗諗<span style=\"color: red;\">為咗用火魔裝修間爛鬼舖頭 就用場運動嘅前途去博</span> 值唔值得博？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人！ 反抗！</span><br />\n<br />\n祝大家可以喺香城online 打爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08da5fa58446ee60b41c308ce101016bacb0d58","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"以下quote咗啲上個post嘅：<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>居民真係無辜 <br />\n唔好話火燒到佢地<br />\n淨係啲煙已經好攞命 夜晚咁燒真係冇教好訓</blockquote>呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n火蠋死人好多時俾煙焗死多過俾火燒死<br />\n而且火勢好難控制到你覺得大火果陣可能已經救唔切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>居民真係無辜 <br />\n唔好話火燒到佢地<br />\n淨係啲煙已經好攞命 夜晚咁燒真係冇教好訓</blockquote>呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n火蠋死人好多時俾煙焗死多過俾火燒死<br />\n而且火勢好難控制到你覺得大火果陣可能已經救唔切</blockquote>只係想講冇人應該因為咁而犧牲<br />\n居民真係好無辜 <br />\n見到前線連富臨啲魚都唔想殺 <br />\n係咪應該諗下樓上住既人值不值得受呢種傷害</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>作為連鎖店高層<br />\n我可以答你<br />\n<br />\n你火燒一次佢最多有排唔開<br />\n但水浸幾次電腦同貨損失仲大<br />\n<br />\n因為你火燒完佢最多唔擺人唔擺貨淨蝕租<br />\n但水浸幾次佢店員又要返工執（蝕薪）<br />\n電腦/貨又要換（蝕貨）<br />\n成日比人攪無生意（蝕租）<br />\n<br />\n如果佢水浸一次就想止蝕唔開？<br />\n咁佢其實咪又係步火燒一樣後果<br />\n<br />\n班暴徒玩火咪好<br />\n藍絲睇完更嬲，政府同大陸又可以作文<br />\n但其實傷害唔算深<br />\n如果燒到平民民意仲會好似67暴動咁逆轉<br />\n<br />\n所以千其唔好玩水啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>想出來做大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係叫就上前線叫啦</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>個人覺得物理裝修就可以 用魔法裝修真係多左<br />\n一來會耗mp (無謂為一兩間鋪仔曬咁多mp,又話魔法野好短缺？）<br />\n最重要係火呢啲野好難控制，一陣消防黎唔切波及埋鋪入面啲石油氣會好好好大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望前線手足可以諗諗佢<br />\n利申 唔割</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>手足一早有共識唔燒鋪<br />\n唔好見到燒鋪就入手足數<br />\n明唔明</blockquote>而家發現店主係黃,你同唔同要籌番間舖比佢?<br />\n同時有需要係民間記者會強調番唔放火e 個共識<br />\n咁先可以入黑警數</blockquote>一定要民間記者會講番<br />\n我地要展示手足們係有制度唔似曱由</blockquote>認同<br />\n民間記招要講返唔再用火裝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>落場叫喇 係到叫把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對唔住啊店主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以眾籌<br />\n定有冇得claim保險</blockquote>真係唔知你地點賠<br />\n同埋有d 野唔係錢解決到<br />\n<br />\n要即刻出聲明 , 誓言唔會亂用火傷及無辜<br />\n<br />\n否則popo 一定繼續扮你地 亂傷無辜</blockquote>只係盡人士咋<br />\n出聲明要搵民間記者會<br />\n同埋要前線肯跟先得<br />\n推到前線睇到</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>落場叫淨係叫到一個，係到叫就係希望多啲人睇到<br />\n前線有同黑警對抗嘅勇氣係好好，更好嘅係有紀律/焦點咁去做嘢</blockquote>冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落場叫唔到幾多<br />\n同埋咁危險嘅情況<br />\n冇人會有心機聽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>前線們紀律係一樣好重要嘅嘢，無嘅就同黑警/義和團無任何分喇<br />\n用火既即刻用水救再射濕入面啲嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我哋唔係暴徒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>核彈都唔割<br />\n但著火就割<br />\n咩核彈黎？</blockquote>睇晒先啦 割<br />\n咪講撚咗唔割<br />\n有鑊一齊揹<br />\n<br />\n但唔完美 可唔可以改善呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>繼續吹奏前線100%唔會做錯<br />\n繼續用核爆都唔割黎勒索和理非<br />\n<br />\n近幾日唔係暴大單野沖一沖根本已經錯到仆街啦<br />\n襟得住連登d質疑聲音出面d人你襟得哂咩?<br />\n燒地鋪燒民居,燒人都做得出...仲要唔俾人講<br />\n唔係痴撚線係咩?<br />\n<br />\n玩埋恐怖襲擊傷及無辜憑咩叫人唔割</blockquote>雖然你係P牌但你講嘅嘢真係好L中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似呢個post講唔好濫用火魔一樣<br />\n有一啲字詞、有啲口號要喺適當嘅時候用亦都唔好攞嚟濫用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫民間記者會公開講明我地有共識係以後裝修唔用火魔法，帶左頭盔先，以後仲有火魔法咪叫大家自己估邊個做囉，但到時我地唔主動割。</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>岩<br />\n就好似之前我地宣傳黑先裝修一樣<br />\n要文宣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>火魔法可唔可以唔好再喺民居樓下既鋪出現</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔撚係想割呀 <br />\n而係太大火係會消死人呀<br />\n講既係人命呀屌你老母</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>裝修既同我做之前諗清楚呀<br />\n做錯一步係成個香港陪你死呀</strong></span></blockquote>人命先至係最重要</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>同意<br />\n對手嘅文宣就係呢d相，甚或樓主冇放嘅片<br />\n火魔搞清楚對象啦，唔係必須嘅何必明知有機會搞到樓上都用呢？場運動真係好多人前途都押左上去架，唔係隨口屌句民意撚就得架，可以避免嘅風險要避免&amp;轉用其他alternative，諗下啦&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>粒核彈有用就話比你放<br />\n粒核彈傷到自己仲多過人 <br />\n講乜撚野割唔割？無腦？<br />\n唔通有人燒哂成條街你又話唔割？</blockquote><blockquote>燒到樓上民居真係會仆街<br />\n同以前菠蘿炸死細路一樣，令運動極速收皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>燒到樓上民居真係會仆街<br />\n同以前菠蘿炸死細路一樣，令運動極速收皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望大家諗清楚<br />\n檢討下所做緊嘅事同我哋嘅初心<br />\n應唔應傷害到無辜嘅人"},{"pid":"cae3e1b9c714f36f0c81489be1c49fcb4be30db1","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58e65a030e65205fa57891918783087b65a3a2eb","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43f2cc958894ce7d3f8234a341ad5a9a03a7bf00","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93152cfba0b573ddcb887900e925e456291e1387","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4c759749fb5e32bd01293d44d02fbb0c20fd378e","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a396237a3236efb2e5f911c28f247a2146486fa4","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac634e2585a84611e2567aa741f73aa1c9633868","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f2994cd6239bc5e4ce6318b484acb3781b5f4131","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"開個正常標題冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d165049fb2379e8fd83bb9284d24c820a83c282","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b5311ecf5e3012b4a4466adbb6476f2b9d896dae","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:30:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d1a1ad90771f1b1ed84403c46658acd2c0555ca7","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:30:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2f38d068460c333a75e36c44d751b2841e7e7cdd","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f2ebc33af5d9f278ed387a14cd97c1c21cf02887","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"395a85f140ac4d402c7cdb77771dca92c3d19831","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:31:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4eb2aba804818f6556965d581012fb88311ff311","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d597c416f5577dd1ed6be7ab54121db5ef028f5","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"696e7bc8520e7e48df9572e3ef1f3410d94cc040","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51c60886bf8438466680f09ca0886cc9467fcd6f","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e5ff937e44e3c390e36d0c45c103e28de3365c8","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3ddd0c9765546bb28c7d1315ecbb75d9c4da2900","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10fdbbc10db98091c57f5ccdbf596877e1b1cc7a","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a8fb567710aaddb751713852cf7446218405019","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4cd6ce039b4204e5fd0c13385a57b968d67f0667","tid":1723354,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"push"}]}